# Venom UI file rules

- Reuse existing classes, tokens, includes, and patterns first.
- Never hardcode colors.
- Never add inline `style=""`.
- Never invent a parallel border/card/button utility system.
- Preserve Smarty variables and conditional logic.
- Keep page-specific CSS local and shared UI shared.
- After UI edits, run `python .kilocode/scripts/theme_guard.py` when terminal access is available.
- Validate dark/light, cyan + one contrasting accent, 375 / 768 / 1024, focus-visible, and CTA honesty.
